# Open Pharmacopoeia - JP18 Edition Metadata
#
# Japanese Pharmacopoeia 18th Edition (JP18)
#
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> .
@prefix dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix op: <https://www.openphar.org/ontology/core/> .
@prefix bib: <https://www.openphar.org/ontology/bibliographic/> .
@prefix edition: <https://www.openphar.org/data/edition/> .
@prefix supplement: <https://www.openphar.org/data/edition/jp/> .

# =============================================================================
# JAPANESE PHARMACOPOEIA 18TH EDITION
# =============================================================================

edition:jp/jp18
    a bib:Edition ;
    skos:prefLabel "Japanese Pharmacopoeia 18th Edition"@en ;
    skos:prefLabel "第十八改正日本薬局方"@ja ;
    skos:altLabel "JP18"@en ;
    skos:altLabel "JP 18"@en ;

    bib:editionNumber "18" ;
    bib:hasPublisher op:JP ;

    # Dates
    bib:publicationDate "2021-06-25"^^xsd:date ;
    bib:effectiveDate "2021-12-01"^^xsd:date ;

    # Statistics
    bib:monographCount 327 ;

    # Official URL
    bib:editionUrl <https://www.mhlw.go.jp/topics/bukyoku/iyaku/yakkyoku/index.html> ;

    # Languages
    bib:officialLanguage "ja" ;
    bib:officialLanguage "en" ;

    # Supplements
    bib:hasSupplement supplement:jp18-supplement1 ;
    bib:hasSupplement supplement:jp18-supplement2 ;

    dct:description """
The Japanese Pharmacopoeia (JP) 18th Edition is the official pharmacopoeia of Japan,
published by the Ministry of Health, Labour and Welfare (MHLW). It contains standards
for pharmaceuticals, including chemical drugs, crude drugs, biological products, and
formulations.

The JP18 includes:
- Official monographs for pharmaceutical substances
- General tests, processes, and apparatus
- Reference spectra (IR and UV)
- Crude drug monographs
- Kampo extract formulations
"""@en .

